    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1939-03-15T00:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1939-03-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="31"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d31">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">860F.00/631: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Czechoslovakia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Carr</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Praha</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-03-15T06:00:00+01:00"
                            >March 15, 1939—6 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 6:20 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>32. The occupation of the remainder of this country by German troops is scheduled
                    to begin at this moment, i. e., 6 a.m.</p>
                <p>The Military Attaché reports that this information has been confirmed by the
                    General Staff.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Carr</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
